  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Void of Lilly comes to Steam for free!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/962084319678aed5151fc1d0b81a861d.poster.avif?t=1773817173\" width=640 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/962084319678aed5151fc1d0b81a861d.webm?t=1773817173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/962084319678aed5151fc1d0b81a861d.mp4?t=1773817173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Long time ago, people faced the Black Fog disease. That's how Axis city became the last bastion of humanity. Years of progress within total isolation, and now it's a beautiful place, filled with advanced techologies. But you aren't really interested in all af this stuff, right? You just want to find your sister and bring her back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a short story-focused game with a few JRPG elements, beautiful pixel art and BULLET-HELL-like battles!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/4babcbe114b8d30612a3c64708c61510.poster.avif?t=1773817173\" width=640 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/4babcbe114b8d30612a3c64708c61510.webm?t=1773817173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/4babcbe114b8d30612a3c64708c61510.mp4?t=1773817173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Ann to find her sister in a short 60-120 minutes adventure</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Hack\" your enemies in Bullet Hell fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the world's mystery</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pet cats</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/2e58c0584ff628fef262967079ae852f.poster.avif?t=1773817173\" width=640 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/2e58c0584ff628fef262967079ae852f.webm?t=1773817173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/2e58c0584ff628fef262967079ae852f.mp4?t=1773817173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Void of Lilly comes to Steam for free!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/962084319678aed5151fc1d0b81a861d.poster.avif?t=1773817173\" width=640 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/962084319678aed5151fc1d0b81a861d.webm?t=1773817173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/962084319678aed5151fc1d0b81a861d.mp4?t=1773817173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Long time ago, people faced the Black Fog disease. That's how Axis city became the last bastion of humanity. Years of progress within total isolation, and now it's a beautiful place, filled with advanced techologies. But you aren't really interested in all af this stuff, right? You just want to find your sister and bring her back!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a short story-focused game with a few JRPG elements, beautiful pixel art and BULLET-HELL-like battles!!!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/4babcbe114b8d30612a3c64708c61510.poster.avif?t=1773817173\" width=640 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/4babcbe114b8d30612a3c64708c61510.webm?t=1773817173\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3866140/extras/4babcbe114b8d30612a3c64708c61510.mp4?t=1773817173\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"